txt.en: Rock-worms can be found on the northern edge of the Gladdenmere.\n\nYou should defeat any rock-worms that you find in the Gladdenmere.
You have defeated many rock-worms in the Gladdenmere, making the Vales of Anduin safer for the Wilderfolk.

Rock-worms patrol the northern edge of the Gladdenmere, from the shoreline to the slopes of the mountains. These beasts have been raised and bred by the stone-giants of the Gladdenmere into vicious pets and should be defeated if the Gladdenmere is to be made safe for the Wilderfolk of the Vales.
The stone-giants of the Gladdenmere raise deadly rock-worms as their pets.
